msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:67
msgid ""
"DMN integration: upload DMN files, deploy to Operaton, and test decision "
"evaluations. `dct:source` placeholder URI for DMN file location, "
"`ronl:implementedBy` for the executing software system, `cpsv:isRequiredBy` "
"back-link to the DMN model. Baseline iKnow integration: parses "
"CognitatieAnnotation and SemanticsExport XML formats, maps to CPSV-AP fields "
"via configurable mappings."
msgstr ""

