msgid "Positioning of the CPSV Editor"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Creference%5Csemantic-mediation-architecture.md:127
msgid ""
"The CPSV Editor operates at the **Business Domain Model** and **Canonical "
"Information Model** levels. It produces CPSV-AP 3.2.0 compliant Turtle files "
"that represent government services using standardised EU and Dutch "
"vocabularies. These artefacts are the canonical representation that the "
"semantic mediation layer uses to bridge to citizen-facing vocabulary."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Creference%5Csemantic-mediation-architecture.md:129
msgid ""
"The RPP architectural pattern (Rules–Policy–Parameters) further decomposes "
"the Business Domain Model level into its governance layers, ensuring that "
"the semantic chain from legislation to citizen communication is fully "
"traceable."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:1
msgid "DMN Testing"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:3
msgid ""
"The DMN tab provides two advanced testing modes in addition to single-"
"request evaluation: intermediate decision tests and test cases. Both are "
"available after a successful deployment and are shown as collapsible "
"sections in the DMN tab."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:7
msgid "Intermediate decision tests"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:9
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor\\user-guide\\dmn-testing.md:9"
msgid "When to use"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:11
msgid ""
"Use intermediate tests when debugging a complex DMN. Rather than examining "
"only the final output, you can verify each sub-decision individually and "
"pinpoint exactly where the logic diverges from expectations."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:13
msgid "How it works"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:15
msgid ""
"After deployment, expand the **Intermediate Decision Tests** section. The "
"editor lists all testable decisions (constant parameters with `p_*` prefix "
"are excluded automatically). Click **Run Intermediate Tests** to evaluate "
"each decision sequentially using the current request body."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:17
msgid "Results display progressively as each decision is evaluated:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:19
msgid ""
"1  leeftijd                   ✅ OK\n"
"2  meerderjarigDezeMaand      ✅ OK\n"
"3  rechtOpToeslag             ✅ OK\n"
"4  inkomenBovenDrempel        ❌ ERROR"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:26
msgid ""
"The section only appears for DMNs with more than one decision — single-table "
"DMNs do not have intermediate decisions to test."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:35
msgid "Test cases"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:37
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor\\user-guide\\dmn-testing.md:37"
msgid "When to use"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:39
msgid ""
"Use test cases for regression testing (verifying the DMN still works after "
"changes), scenario validation (edge cases and business rule coverage), and "
"as living test documentation."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:41
msgid "Preparing a test cases file"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:43
msgid ""
"Create a JSON file containing an array of test cases. Two formats are "
"supported:"
