#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:120
msgid "Debugging strategy"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:122
msgid "Work from simple to complex:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:124
msgid ""
"**Single evaluate** — Verify the request body is correct and the model "
"responds."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:125
msgid ""
"**Intermediate tests** — Identify which sub-decision produces an unexpected "
"result."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:126
msgid "**Test cases** — Validate complete scenarios including edge cases."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:128
msgid "Watch the browser console for extraction logs:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:130
msgid ""
"[DMN Parse] Filtered 8 constant parameter(s), kept 12 testable decision(s)\n"
"[DMN] Extracted primary decision key: \"zorgtoeslag_resultaat\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:137
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor\\user-guide\\dmn-testing.md:137"
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:139
msgid ""
"**All intermediate tests show ERROR** — Verify deployment status shows "
"\"Deployed — ID: ...\". Check that variable names in the request body match "
"the `<inputData name=\"...\">` values in the DMN XML."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:141
msgid ""
"**Test cases fail to parse** — Ensure the file is valid JSON, that the top "
"level is an array (`[...]` not `{...}`), and that you are using one of the "
"two supported formats."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:143
msgid ""
"**Empty request body generated** — The DMN XML has no `<inputData>` elements "
"or they are malformed. Use **Load Example** to see the expected structure, "
"then compare to your DMN file."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-testing.md:145
msgid ""
"**Date conversion error** — Change `\"type\": \"Date\"` to `\"type\": "
"\"String\"` for date value fields."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:1
msgid "DMN Workflow"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:3
msgid ""
"This guide walks through uploading, deploying, testing, and exporting a DMN "
"decision model as part of a service definition."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:7
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor\\user-guide\\dmn-workflow.md:7"
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:9
msgid "A `.dmn` file (DMN 1.3 XML format)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:10
msgid ""
"The service metadata tabs (Service, Organisation, Legal) filled in — the "
"service identifier is used to construct DMN URIs"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:11
msgid ""
"Access to the Operaton rule engine (default: `https://operaton.open-"
"regels.nl`)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:15
msgid "Step 1: Upload the DMN file"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:17
msgid ""
"In the **DMN tab**, click **Upload DMN File** and select your `.dmn` file."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:19
msgid "On upload, the editor:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:21
msgid "Parses all `<decision>` elements from the XML"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:22
msgid "Filters out constant parameters (`p_*` prefix) automatically"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:23
msgid "Extracts the primary decision key (the main output decision)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:24
msgid "Auto-generates a test request body from the `<inputData>` elements"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:25
msgid ""
"Shows a badge: \"N testable decisions detected (p_* constants filtered)\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:27
msgid ""
"If you do not have a DMN file yet, click **Load Example** to use the "
"provided AOW example."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:31
msgid "Step 2: Review the syntactic validation result"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:33
msgid ""
"Immediately after upload, the editor runs the file through the five-layer "
"syntactic validator and displays the result in the file card."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:35
msgid ""
"**If the file is valid**, a green *Syntax valid* badge appears. Any warnings "
"or informational messages are shown in a collapsed panel — review them "
"before deploying."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:37
msgid ""
"**If the file has errors**, the panel expands automatically and lists the "
"issues grouped by layer. Address the errors in your DMN authoring tool "
"before proceeding with deployment."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:39
msgid "Badge"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:39
msgid "Meaning"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:39
msgid "🟢 Syntax valid"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:39
msgid "No errors. Warnings and info messages may still be present."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:39
msgid "🔴 Validation failed"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:39
msgid ""
"One or more errors detected. Deployment will likely fail or produce "
"incorrect results."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:44
msgid ""
"!!! tip Warnings in the **Interaction Rules** layer often indicate orphaned "
"`<inputData>` elements — inputs that exist in the DRD but are not connected "
"to any decision via `<informationRequirement>`. These are harmless for "
"execution but result in dead data in the model."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:47
msgid ""
"For a full explanation of every issue code and its rationale, see the [DMN "
"Validation Reference]{1}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:51
msgid "Step 3: Configure the API endpoint"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:53
msgid ""
"The API endpoint defaults to `https://operaton.open-regels.nl/engine-rest`. "
"Change it if you are using a different Operaton instance."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:57
msgid "Step 4: Deploy to Operaton"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:59
msgid ""
"Click **Deploy to Operaton**. The editor sends the DMN file to the engine "
"via `POST /engine-rest/deployment/create`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:61
msgid ""
"On success, the button changes to **Deployed — ID: {deployment-id}** and the "
"deployment ID and timestamp are stored. These are included in the Turtle "
"output."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:65
msgid "Step 5: Test the decision"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:67
msgid ""
"Review the auto-generated request body in the test panel. Edit variable "
"values to match your test scenario."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:69
msgid ""
"Click **Evaluate Decision** to call `POST /engine-rest/decision-definition/"
"key/{decisionKey}/evaluate`. The response is displayed inline."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:71
msgid ""
"For multi-table DMNs, expand the **Intermediate Decision Tests** section and "
"click **Run Intermediate Tests** to evaluate each sub-decision individually "
"— useful for isolating which part of a complex DRD is producing an "
"unexpected result."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:75
msgid "Step 6: Export TTL with DMN metadata"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:77
msgid "Click **Download TTL**. The exported file includes:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:79
msgid "The `cprmv:DecisionModel` entity with deployment ID and API endpoint"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:80
msgid "All input variables as `cpsv:Input` entities"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:81
msgid ""
"All extracted decision rules as `cprmv:DecisionRule` entities, each linked "
"to the relevant legal article via `cprmv:extends`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:83
msgid "The DMN section is appended after the core service metadata."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:87
msgid "Tips"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:89
msgid ""
"Fill in the Service identifier before uploading the DMN — it is used to "
"construct the DMN model URI."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:90
msgid ""
"Use descriptive decision keys in your DMN XML (e.g. `zorgtoeslag_resultaat` "
"rather than `Decision_1`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:91
msgid "Do not use spaces in decision keys — use underscores or camelCase."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:92
msgid ""
"Deploy and test before exporting. Undeployed DMN metadata in the Turtle "
"output has no deployment ID, which limits its usefulness."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cdmn-workflow.md:93
msgid ""
"Resolve all validation **errors** before deploying. **Warnings** are "
"advisory and will not prevent a successful deployment."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:1
msgid "Filling In the Tabs"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:3
msgid ""
"This page describes each tab's fields, what they map to in the generated "
"Turtle, and what validation rules apply. For the full UI field ↔ RDF "
"property mapping tables, see the [Field Mapping Reference]{1}."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:7
msgid "Service tab"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:9
msgid "The Service tab models `cpsv:PublicService`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:11
msgid ""
"**Unique identifier** (`dct:identifier`) — Mandatory. Used as the base for "
"all URIs in the file. Spaces are converted to hyphens automatically. Choose "
"a stable, human-readable value."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:13
msgid ""
"**Official name** (`dct:title`) — Mandatory. The public-facing name of the "
"service, stored with `@nl` language tag."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:15
msgid ""
"**Description** (`dct:description`) — Detailed explanation of what the "
"service does."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:17
msgid ""
"**Thematic area** (`cv:thematicArea`) — URI for thematic classification. "
"Select from the dropdown or enter a URI directly."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:19
msgid ""
"**Government level** (`cv:sector`) — Mandatory. Select from the controlled "
