msgid "**Organisation name** (`skos:prefLabel`) — The official name."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:39
msgid ""
"**Geographic jurisdiction** (`cv:spatial`) — Mandatory. The geographic area "
