msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:76
msgid ""
"**Valid from / until** (`ronl:validFrom`, `ronl:validUntil`) — Temporal "
