#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:94
msgid ""
"**Unit** (`schema:unitCode`) — The unit of measurement (e.g. `ANN` for "
