msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:96
msgid "**Valid from / until** — Temporal validity."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:100
