msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cuser-guide%5Cfilling-in-the-tabs.md:106
msgid ""
"**Situation** (`cprmv:situatie`) — The contextual situation to which the "
